node.text: I told my mama when i was 17 I was gonna Retire her. Today i surprised her with a early retirement 🥲 at 22 yrs old not many can say that. Now Both of my parents are retired 😌and All of my goals have been accomplished before 25 time to start a new list 💅🏾 #GetThatBreadQuitYoJobAndLeave
